	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another trick with harmony. <br><br>Sometimes you cant harmony creatures on top of something (like aviaks in SK or spectres in oasis) because it says you you are too far aways.<br><br>In this case just go close under the mobs, target yourself and cast harmony on you. The mobs upstairs will all be harmonized. <br><br>Good pulling...<br><br>--------------<br>Wolas<br>44 Wood elf Druid<br>Antonious Bayle<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
