<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101643702157829></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101643702157829><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=101643702157829>RE: Spell Organization</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=101643702157829#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=95215><span id= >Kothall</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>54 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Mar 18th 2:39 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.92]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Mine is done fairly easy.&nbsp;&nbsp;Flip to pages 30+ and that is where all my old, out of date spells start (I move them there as I go).<br><br>Pages 1 and 2 are my stock spells that I almost always load -- <br>     Personal Protect<br>     Skin<br>     Str buff<br>     Heal<br>     Root <br>     Snare<br>     DOT<br>     DD <br>     SoW<br>     Wolf Form<br><br>Pages 3 and 4 are my more single target buff type spells (forgive me, at my level, I have more variety and need to load slightly differently than you may).<br><br>     Regen<br>     Damage Shield<br>     Gate<br>     Bind<br>     Water Breathing<br>     Leviatate<br>     Cure Poison<br>     Cure Disease<br>     Secondary DOT<br>     Secondary DD (Fury of Air)<br><br>Page 5 is all my resists:<br>     Magic<br>     Poison<br>     Disease<br>     Fire<br>     Cold<br><br>Page 6 are my group buffs (you may not have many at your level but...)<br>     Regen<br>     Damage Shield<br>     Skin<br>     SoW<br>     Wolf Form<br><br>Pages 7, 8 and 9 are my Ring spells.<br><br>Page 10 is miscelaneous spells (AoE's, etc...)<br><br>Pages 11, 12, 13 and 14 are my Group Port spells.<br><br>So on and so forth...<br><br>As I get a new generation of spell, I move my older ones back out of the way.  There is a tad bit of a mix up with some of my spells being as Post 50 DOTs and pre-50's stack.  Plus I can't use post 50 buffs on lowbies so I have a few of the older gen in earlier pages because I get a lot of requests on them but this should give you an idea on how you may want to order your book.<br><br>Best bet is to get a few more answers and then reorg your book to best suite your needs.<br><br>Kothall Landrunner<br>55th Preserver -- Povar server.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
