	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a 17 halfling, and moved to the Karanas at 16.<br>1. Travelling between RV and the Karanas is too hard at this level, easier if you get bound at the bank in S.Qeynos.<br><br>2. I'm working almost exclusively in WK.&nbsp;&nbsp;For experience, work the scarecrows on the Miller farm.  Great place to practice kiting and try out your different spells.  (Treeform is great here.)<br><br>3. For loot, try the bandits.  They're easy to kill, have bronze weapons, and drop sashes you can turn in in SQ for 2-3 plat each.<br><br>The shops near the guard post at the road to Miller farm give very good prices, at least as good as in SQ.<br><br>Alternative: take the boat to Erud's Crossing, get off and spend a couple (EQ) days killing wisps.  I made 90 pp there in 2 evenings.<br><br>Danco - Halfling druid 17<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
